notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-9o4","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":5394,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/19\/dua-for-eid\/","url_meta":{"origin":36088,"position":0},"title":"Abu Umamah on Eid: Companions ask Allah to accept good deeds","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 19, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Muhammad ibn Ziyad reported: I was with Abu Umamah al-Bahili and others among the Companions of the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him. When they would return from Eid prayer, they would say to each other, \u201cMay Allah accept good deeds from us and from you.\u201d Imam Ahmad said,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":36091,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/05\/11\/hasan-taqabbal-allahu-minna\/","url_meta":{"origin":36088,"position":1},"title":"Hasan on Eid: May Allah accept from us and from you","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 11, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Hawshab ibn \u2018Aqil reported: I met Al-Hasan al-Basri, may Allah have mercy on him, on the day of Eid and I said, \u201cMay Allah accept good deeds from us and from you.\u201d Al-Hasan said, \u201cYes, may Allah accept good deeds from us and from you.\u201d Source: al-Du\u2019a\u0304\u2019 li-T\u0323abara\u0304ni 930 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":36093,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/05\/11\/companions-taqabbal-allah\/","url_meta":{"origin":36088,"position":2},"title":"Sahaba on Eid: May Allah accept from us and you","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 11, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Jubayr ibn Nufayr reported: The Companions of the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, when they met each other on the day of Eid, they would say to each other, \u201cMay Allah accept good deeds from us and from you.\u201d Source: S\u0323ala\u0304t al-'\u012adayn lil-Mah\u0323a\u0304mili\u0304 2\/218 Grade: Hasan\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34608,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/11\/30\/umar-ii-humility-allah\/","url_meta":{"origin":36088,"position":3},"title":"Umar II on Humility: Best Muslims are humble with Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 30, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Ghazali reported: Umar ibn Abdul Aziz, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cThe best people are those who are humble before Allah.\u201d Source: Ih\u0323ya\u0304\u2019 Ulu\u0304m al-Di\u0304n 3\/355 \u0639\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u063a\u0632\u0627\u0644\u064a \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e \u0639\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064e \u0628\u0652\u0646\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0639\u064e\u0632\u0650\u064a\u0632\u0650 \u0631\u062d\u0645\u0647 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647 \u0642\u0627\u0644 \u062e\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0633\u0650 \u0645\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0643\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e \u0639\u0650\u0646\u0652\u062f\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0